 returns to the beginning again).
 Finally there is a setting for the Prepare Takes function to either use
 the old random coloring method or the newer color scheme that uses blues
 for destination material and greens for source material.
 There will be more on these settings in subsequent sections of the manual.
 If you are unfamiliar with these concepts, I recommend a quick internet
 search! If in doubt, just use the default values.
 It is worth noting that these preferences are set per project.
