\begin_layout Subsection
Automatic Backups
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
REAPER allows for powerful and complex backup routines.
 As referenced above, ReaClassical defaults to 10 time-stamped backups and
 10 auto-saves every 15 minutes when not recording.
 Feel free to modify for your own way of working including switching to
 backups and autosaves for a number of unique days.
\end_layout

